reviewText: thank you very much for a very interesting journey to negotiating processes

An excellent course that helps people better understand the intricacies of negotiation. The excellent, lively presentation makes the course engaging and interesting. And the knowledge test, in the form of tests and creative questions, makes you understand what you need to pay extra attention to. I am very grateful to the creators of such a wonderful opportunity to listen to such a unique and useful course. Thank you.
